name: Successfully place an order by registering during the checkout process
fullName: cypress/e2e/PlaceOrderWithRegistrationDuringCheckout.feature#Place Order with Registration During Checkout Successfully place an order by registering during the checkout process

steps.name: Given I launch the browser and navigate to "https://automationexercise.com"
Then I should see the home page visible successfully
When I add products to the cart
And I click the Cart button as unregistered
Then I should see the cart page displayed
assert expected <li.active> to contain Shopping Cart
When I click the Proceed To Checkout button as unregistered
And I click the Register or Login button
And I fill all details in Signup and create an account

steps.name: Then I should see ACCOUNT CREATED and click the Continue button
assert expected <b> to contain Account Created!
Then I should see Logged in as username at the top
assert expected <a> to contain Logged in as Reinhold
When I click the Cart button as registered
And I click the Proceed To Checkout button as registered
Then I should see Address Details and Review Your Order
When I enter a description in the comment text area and click the Place Order button
And I enter payment details including Name on Card, Card Number, CVC, and Expiration date
